{"tid":513630,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性討論] 大家點睇2018年樓市？","createTime":"2017-12-29T17:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T00:12:31.000Z","uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fead0f6ece462878df741b52908ecd8b7373520f","tid":513630,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T17:22:53.000Z","msg":"話就話美國加息，但香港同唔同步係一個問題，就算加，供樓多幾千蚊坦白講大部分人都負擔到。<br />\n<br />\n香港剛性需求太大，結婚上車、內地走資；明年新盤又唔多，邊有可能唔繼續升？<br />\n<br />\n唯一樓價會跌就係又出現環球經濟危機或者打仗，但兩樣野可能性都不大，各國股市PE唔高、最有可能打仗既北韓同美國都係口水戰多<br />\n<br />\n以上意見拋磚引玉，大家又點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c6a85adcd8497392b834c9dd9d3d9107c29dd3","tid":513630,"uid":17738,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:14:58.000Z","msg":"跌9成好似係"},{"pid":"cf596bb300bb951232d59a911933776e389a53fb","tid":513630,"uid":7447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0c6a85adcd8497392b834c9dd9d3d9107c29dd3","tid":513630,"uid":17738,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:14:58.000Z","msg":"跌9成好似係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T11:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc720a478c0f05956d65a050998d3836e1392716","tid":513630,"uid":86433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T13:36:56.000Z","msg":"覺得等港股跌之後會跟住進入下大幅回調"},{"pid":"d3855f765ff78aaead26a1b0de5d815947feb21f","tid":513630,"uid":35660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T00:34:03.000Z","msg":"同屋企住既咪等下 又可以儲錢<br />\n<br />\n自己搬出來就唔好租啦 <br />\n買到就買 <br />\n<br />\n正正常常 一年都無左 12萬租金<br />\n自己計下啦"},{"pid":"7937dd41e4fe0958cb20785bff4199db79a30719","tid":513630,"uid":44534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T04:53:52.000Z","msg":"要問林太 我係專家就覺得微升10% 左右"},{"pid":"638daaba201b7f7a83e2869fd780c6851d4a8525","tid":513630,"uid":42314,"like":0